# Drop your rendered 3D video here.
#
# MAIN scroll-scrubbed hero (igloo.inc style):
#   filename: scroll-3d.mp4   (referenced by <ScrollVideo> in src/App.jsx)
#   Scroll position drives playback frame-by-frame — so render a clean,
#   self-contained 0->end animation (no need to loop).
#
# Encoding tips for smooth scroll-scrubbing (esp. on mobile/iOS):
#   - H.264 MP4, yuv420p, faststart
#   - Short keyframe interval so seeking is cheap (a keyframe every ~5-10 frames)
#     e.g. ffmpeg:  -c:v libx264 -pix_fmt yuv420p -g 6 -movflags +faststart
#   - 1080p or 720p, ~8-20s, muted, < ~10-15 MB
#   - Also export a poster frame (scroll-3d-poster.jpg) if you want a first frame.
#
# Optional extra panels (static): disassemble.mp4 / seam.mp4 / disclose.mp4
# referenced by <VideoSection> — set their src in src/App.jsx.
